54.1	Kevin_Trudeau	Kevin Trudeau	Kevin Mark Trudeau (born February 6, 1963) is an American author, radio personality, and infomercial salesman best known for promoting alternative medicine. A number of his television infomercials and several of his books, including Natural Cures "They" Don't Want You to Know About, allege that both the U.S. Food and Drug Administration and the pharmaceutical industry value profit more highly than treatments or cures.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0a/Kevin_Trudeau_cropped.JPG
